title: Trump denies seeing Navarro memos warning about toll of coronavirus
description: President Trump said at a press briefing Tuesday that he "didn't see" memos from his trade adviser Peter Navarro warning in January and February that the coronavirus crisis could kill more than half a million Americans and cost close to $6 trillion. Why it ma…
content:
